plyTime":"2018-02-23T03:19:19.000Z","msg":"個一千蚊, 用淨比番佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed33c159b8b2c6e50e9b91be38c47fe3e56462a","tid":568893,"uid":11523,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:22:50.000Z","msg":"請老豆飲茶囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家都係<br />\n以前細個無乜錢洗<br />\n啲利是袋晒洗晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家大左賺到錢<br />\n咪拎啲出黎請阿爸阿媽飲下茶<br />\n得閒去果欄買啲生果番黎氹下佢地開心<br />\n佢地已經開心成日 好滿足架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208f1b619d292f1e63d2d28e301f74d4c4868562","tid":568893,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"你阿爸想你自覺啲，唔洗下下要佢提點先鬧你下化？對你有要求"},{"pid":"a4cb14fc0cb04443918139e678fb1d349bf5a06b","tid":568893,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T22:52:31.000Z","msg":"細佬，老豆封完比你，有冇問你拎番二百，佢話無錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a8fba9ebf9f0c20a0b38b2e862b894a5732098","tid":568893,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4cb14fc0cb04443918139e678fb1d349bf5a06b","tid":568893,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T22:52:31.000Z","msg":"細佬，老豆封完比你，有冇問你拎番二百，佢話無錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T23:03:27.000Z","msg":"我覺得果一千利事係老豆當入銀行咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb26cca6caa557da52692ceca04336af11e37be8","tid":568893,"uid":6115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1293c606a9e47c83835975ed74f0a7780431431","tid":568893,"uid":64925,"like":1,"dislike":80,"score":-79,"quote":{"pid":"97d